14:28:07.929 [INFO] # Finance record frontmatter

14:28:07.929 [INFO] Finance notes are gradually migrating toward YAML frontmatter so they stay readable in Obsidian while exposing structured fields for automation.

14:28:07.929 [INFO] When a task asks you to OCR, normalize, or structure a finance note:

14:28:07.929 [INFO] - extract visible data from the existing note body into YAML frontmatter
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - preserve the existing note body below the frontmatter as the source OCR or human-readable content
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - do not invent fields that are not supported by the visible note
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - if the visible invoice or bill data does not mention a currency, assume euros for `total_eur`, `unit_eur`, and `line_eur`

14:28:07.929 [INFO] ## Invoice schema

14:28:07.929 [INFO] For invoices, add YAML frontmatter like this:

14:28:07.929 [INFO] ```yaml
14:28:07.929 [INFO] ---
14:28:07.929 [INFO] record_type: invoice
14:28:07.929 [INFO] invoice_number: INV-0017
14:28:07.929 [INFO] alias: northstar-renewal
14:28:07.929 [INFO] issued_on: 2026-03-10
14:28:07.929 [INFO] total_eur: 4200
14:28:07.929 [INFO] counterparty: Northstar Forecasting
14:28:07.929 [INFO] project: Forecast Recovery Sprint
14:28:07.929 [INFO] related_entity: Mila Novak
14:28:07.929 [INFO] lines:
14:28:07.929 [INFO]   - item: Discovery workshop
14:28:07.929 [INFO]     quantity: 2
14:28:07.929 [INFO]     unit_eur: 900
14:28:07.929 [INFO]     line_eur: 1800
14:28:07.929 [INFO]   - item: Model tuning
14:28:07.929 [INFO]     quantity: 3
14:28:07.929 [INFO]     unit_eur: 800
14:28:07.929 [INFO]     line_eur: 2400
14:28:07.929 [INFO] ---
14:28:07.929 [INFO] ```

14:28:07.929 [INFO] Required invoice fields:

14:28:07.929 [INFO] - `record_type`
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - `invoice_number`
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - `alias`
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - `issued_on`
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - `total_eur`
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - `counterparty`
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - `project`
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - `lines`

14:28:07.929 [INFO] Optional invoice fields:

14:28:07.929 [INFO] - `related_entity`

14:28:07.929 [INFO] Invoice line rules:

14:28:07.929 [INFO] - `lines` is an ordered list and should follow the visible line-item order from the note
14:28:07.929 [INFO] - each line item must include:
14:28:07.929 [INFO]   - `item`
14:28:07.929 [INFO]   - `quantity`
